</head>
<body>
  <div class="ambient ambient-a"></div>
  <div class="ambient ambient-b"></div>
  <div class="ambient ambient-c"></div>

  <main class="app-shell">
    <section id="homeView" class="view active home-view">
      <nav class="top-nav">
        <div class="brand-mark">Pair Aura</div>
        <button class="ghost-btn small" id="jumpToInputBtn">直接生成</button>
      </nav>

      <div class="hero-orbit" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="aura aura-left"><span>A</span></div>
        <div class="aura aura-right"><span>B</span></div>
        <div class="aura-core"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">RELATIONSHIP AURA REPORT</p>
        <h1>测测你和 TA<br />是哪种关系气场</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">输入两个人的 MBTI / SBTI 类型，生成合拍指数、冲突点、相处建议和可转发海报。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <button class="primary-btn" id="startBtn">开始合成关系</button>
        <button class="secondary-btn" id="loadDemoBtn">看一个示例</button>
      </div>

      <div class="sample-tags">
        <span>高吸引高摩擦型</span>
        <span>互补成长型</span>
        <span>稳定同频型</span>
        <span>需要翻译型</span>
      </div>
    </section>

